<item>
 <title>Humour in Popular Songs for Kids</title>
 <link>https://vse.la/blog/humour-popular-songs-kids</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Pen pineapple apple pen&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This song was so popular when just issued. &lt;a href=&quot;/pikotaro/ppap-pen-pineapple-apple-pen&quot;&gt;Lyrics here&lt;/a&gt;. It makes you smile over a man that makes first steps in English language. Don&#039;t be confused with words that sound alike! Have a short hint and listen seriously:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;P-P-A-P!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is an abbreviation for the next sentence. This way song sharpens attention of listeners. Next it explains in detail its short meaning:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have a pen, I have a apple&lt;br /&gt;
Uh! Apple-pen!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have a pen, I have pineapple&lt;br /&gt;
Uh! Pineapple-pen!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Kids may learn how to combine parts of words and use it for create different words.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Next the song is playing the game with its own rules, creating multifunctional word &quot;pen-pineapple-apple-pen&quot;. This is the end point of a lesson.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Bananaphone&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you are a bit sad, listen this person that is very confident he creates something wonderful. Feel the vibe. &lt;a href=&quot;/raffi/bananaphone&quot;&gt;Lyrics here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ring ring ring ring ring ring ring banana phone&lt;br /&gt;
Ring ring ring ring ring ring ring banana phone&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This song may fill any place. Do you want to call for pizza? Do you want to chat with a white house? Where is the cat?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&#039;ll call for pizza. I&#039;ll call my cat&lt;br /&gt;
I&#039;ll call the white house, have a chat&lt;br /&gt;
I&#039;ll place a call around the world, operator get me Bejing-jing-jing-jing&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are no borders. Restrictions are not real with such a device you found. Bananaphone is something crazy!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Heiko &amp;amp; Meiko - Glücklich&lt;/h2&gt;

